+
+## 5. Activity Screen Copy
+
+### Labels
+
+| Element | Copy |
+|---------|------|
+| Section header | `Activity` |
+| Search placeholder | `Search transactions` |
+
+### Filter chips
+
+Stock set for V1. Sentence case.
+
+| Group | Chip labels |
